<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Holotype of Pyropia columbiensis. South end of West Beach, Calvert Island, British Columbia, Canada, S. C. Lindstrom 15596, 18 Feb 2014, UBC A 90636." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.52.5009.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/45750" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
